{"id":317787,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-林秀丽、初东芳因撒传单被拘留期满获释/","date":"2013-10-13T15:48:14Z","modified":"2013-10-13T15:48:14Z","title":"维权网 | 林秀丽、初东芳因撒传单被拘留期满获释（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）山东青岛林秀丽</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日，在天安门金水桥撒传单抗议司法腐败，被北京市公安局天安门分局以“扰乱公共秩序”为由行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。林秀丽是一起刑事案件的受害人，她被罪犯掐晕后，从六楼窗户仍下。邻居报警经抢救方才保住了性命。法院在审判此案时枉法判决，罪犯至今逍遥法外。而林秀丽因此上访维权，却被当地打击报复，被关精神病院，被非法关押，她多次以绝食方式抗争非法关押。特别是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月林秀丽在北京南站巧遇温家宝总理又被被青岛市政府、法院强迫失踪一年多。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黑龙江佳木斯的初东芳因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日长假期间，在北京钓鱼台国宾馆因实施撒传单喊口号等反腐行为，被北京公安局朝阳分局以“扰乱公共秩序”为由行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。维权访民初东方因其哥哥初少才，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日劝架，被卷入到一起刑事案件中，被判无期徒刑。而初东方为此上访告状，初东方说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>“哥哥案件的讯问笔录都是伪造的，鉴定结果证明哥哥初少才的讯问笔录非本人签字时，（现有字迹鉴定书证实）。本案定罪没有物证。公检法采信伪证判哥哥初少才无期徒刑。因此我对本案不服上访维权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日是她们拘留期满的释放日，维权访民们自发到北京市拘留所迎接林秀丽、初东芳。大家表示：我们一定要团结一致，守望相助，共同反腐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><span>前去迎接林秀丽、初东芳的维权人士有：黑龙江于丽华、吕双丽，吉林邓志波，江苏吴继新，内蒙赵玉富，河南李明翠，辽宁王素娥、杨秀梅、宋殿芬等人。</span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zYt9WlHUQOk/Ulq0gINp48I/AAAAAAAApeM/pjR3S3J_PdY/s1600/11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zYt9WlHUQOk/Ulq0gINp48I/AAAAAAAApeM/pjR3S3J_PdY/s320/11.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SEW3tB7Q-9c/Ulq0k4LGuTI/AAAAAAAApec/BbZtbO3QVkc/s1600/22.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SEW3tB7Q-9c/Ulq0k4LGuTI/AAAAAAAApec/BbZtbO3QVkc/s320/22.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-C5myzlDCkhM/Ulq0jX_diCI/AAAAAAAApeU/hREjubtluI0/s1600/33.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-C5myzlDCkhM/Ulq0jX_diCI/AAAAAAAApeU/hREjubtluI0/s320/33.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}